{"tid":2429732,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"葉劉淑儀: 現任行政長官設立的創新與統籌辦事處確是失敗之作，成員在辦公室內設立連儂牆，實在匪夷所思","createTime":"2021-03-02T13:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T05:25:56.000Z","uid":167469,"like":58,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"85bd8f45b68479383f315750ac9d199e3c580229","tid":2429732,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:38:42.000Z","msg":"香港應如何變革？（二）<br />\n<br />\n上文提到數碼革命使全球發展格局產生大變，中國經濟的崛起衝擊香港的長遠競爭力及管治文化，香港要與時並進，需從改革政府架構做起。<br />\n<br />\n談到架構，廢除中央政策組讓人遺憾。特區政府於一九八○年代研究設立中央政策組時，曾諮詢各政策科和部門，當時很多政務官，包括我也覺得增設這個「組」是「多個香爐多隻鬼」，擔心「街外人」會與政務官意見相左，不欲政府以外的學者、專家參與制訂政策的過程。後來，中央政策組正式成立，以負責策略性思考、諮詢、制訂研究方向、蒐集及分析民意等工作為主，為因循守舊的政府注入新思維，發揮作為特區政府智囊的角色。我認為在歷屆中策組首席顧問裏，劉兆佳教授最為稱職。這位資深學者在任期間既頻做民調以進行研究工作，也會邀請內地及海外學者來港，促進政府策略性思維。<br />\n<br />\n民間智庫在培訓政策研究及政治人才上有重要角色，美國的智庫更以「旋轉門」形式運行，不少部長級官員來自智庫，用他們的學說制訂政策，辭官後便重回智庫工作。於是很多智庫均獲大企業資助，研究工作形成產業，各種學說百花齊放。香港的情况則難以比擬。<br />\n<br />\n現任特首上任時，設立政策創新與統籌辦事處取代中策組，並改由政務官擔任總監。當時我已覺這職權編制會使決策及行事重返以往「由上至下」的老調，喪失中策組的功能。<strong><span class=\"red\">此外，雖然特首有心吸納年輕人為研究政策工作提出嶄新角度，但是在實際操作上，創新辦的年輕人學歷、閱歷和經驗尚淺，缺乏策略性思維訓練，不可與中策組的專家學者們比擬。最匪夷所思的是，據悉黑暴期間，竟有創新辦成員在辦公室內設立連儂牆，公然無視公職人員要向政府效忠的責任。且創新辦成立至今也不見得有何嶄新及富建設性的建議，可見確是失敗之作。</span></strong>我建議下屆政府恢復設立中策組，延攬來自不同背景、研究不同範疇的高學歷人才，為香港發展作出實際貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n香港應如何變革？（二）(撰文: 葉劉淑儀，原文刊載於明報)<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/作家專欄/article/20210226/s00018/1614276729734/香港應如何變革-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E4%BD%9C%E5%AE%B6%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84%2Farticle%2F20210226%2Fs00018%2F1614276729734%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%87%89%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%AE%8A%E9%9D%A9-&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQAwKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=025d0fed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E4%BD%9C%E5%AE%B6%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84%2Farticle%2F20210226%2Fs00018%2F1614276729734%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%87%89%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%AE%8A%E9%9D%A9-&h=d9995d8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/作家專欄/article/20210226/s00018/1614276729734/香港應如何變革-</a>（二）?fbclid=IwAR394ASIFxFWXrgjDRqyA6tJbdog9M6tzlJd1FwPSyrXSAjgHiKnQPfmzZ0<br />\n<br />\nsource: 葉劉淑儀facebook"},{"pid":"2ee6cf4ce2ca1e77e328bf5fe1c34e64d3b1d967","tid":2429732,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:39:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"66898286366aef1a74f6fd0fb868eb80356c1651","tid":2429732,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:39:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9184662d5261edf8286199896a950b7101be25df","tid":2429732,"uid":79563,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有創新辦成員在辦公室內設立連儂牆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e878ee05f492e7a2c07eb5085c5fb29efb4c178","tid":2429732,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:40:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0ee55ab7fb38af7146b1b9987838cffed70c51a0","tid":2429732,"uid":383344,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:41:23.000Z","msg":"延攬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676b3be8c03f17c94df4713f98de407ea5505b7e","tid":2429732,"uid":51271,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:42:01.000Z","msg":"果頭話要吹和風，唔好再鬥班AO、公務員，點知自己都比足油<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0R38vbC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0R38vbC.gif&h=21a22440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n★支那好治癒gif貼圖區！（10）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/snbAPRX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/snbAPRX</a>"},{"pid":"2661673293a314a16fd5903fa7d469f5d15bcede","tid":2429732,"uid":36238,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2481738/org/0b20ad84fcae4b2b687747e815f491ed.jpg/gHBTDqSPMgO_4a0rCMO0IRX2Tbo6VsImgHzz1YB889U?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2481738%2Forg%2F0b20ad84fcae4b2b687747e815f491ed.jpg%2FgHBTDqSPMgO_4a0rCMO0IRX2Tbo6VsImgHzz1YB889U%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=99e77b28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9695d9518f1b744ee8138148020756367f3e3d6","tid":2429732,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4af4ace7fb4bc656482ad1aa4174d73dd0e81f8e","tid":2429732,"uid":282637,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:43:29.000Z","msg":"連儂牆係衰野,國際大都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6680834c5387c1d3aa98a8f53997826f5f102c","tid":2429732,"uid":135169,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"quote":{"pid":"2661673293a314a16fd5903fa7d469f5d15bcede","tid":2429732,"uid":36238,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2481738/org/0b20ad84fcae4b2b687747e815f491ed.jpg/gHBTDqSPMgO_4a0rCMO0IRX2Tbo6VsImgHzz1YB889U?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2481738%2Forg%2F0b20ad84fcae4b2b687747e815f491ed.jpg%2FgHBTDqSPMgO_4a0rCMO0IRX2Tbo6VsImgHzz1YB889U%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=99e77b28&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:43:34.000Z","msg":"啲內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁都有得批鬥<br />\n幾時禁止香港出售post-it"},{"pid":"5f5f989a04bdbc15bb8659a580745429262d3ef7","tid":2429732,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:44:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a5098b0b369f476e1128277ec95005249187f921","tid":2429732,"uid":282637,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:45:09.000Z","msg":"[二等公民][利用港人]葉劉女兒:我覺得美國生活較適合我<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2391977\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2391977</a><br />\n留港兩年<br />\n葉榮欣穿上超低胸Tee和牛仔褲，自己揹着一大袋衫，與新民黨公關前來。拍照前，她刻意換了成熟的連身裙和四吋高跟鞋，除去稚味。她先帶記者和攝影師導賞新立法會，<span class=\"red\">「這裏雖然大，但我成日撞到其他議員，同泛民的會啱傾些，好似不同黨的劉慧卿（民主黨），一齊食過飯；搭「車立」撞過葉國謙（民建聯），大家無嘢講。」</span><br />\n<br />\n以前每逢學校假期，葉榮欣都會返港，在黨內做義工，大學畢業後更決定留港兩年，先幫母親打江山，之後再返美國讀MBA。她老實說：<span class=\"red\">「我覺得美國生活較適合我，因為講英文，無人識我媽咪。留在香港是因為她，尖子人才好難留，我的作用會大過在美國。」</span><br />\n<br />\n代母出征<br />\n她今年七月正式受薪上班，每朝十時前返到公司，主力負責策劃和宣傳，收工後還要陪母親去宴會、飯局應酬。遇正母親有事未能出席，她更要代母出席，孤身上陣。問她是否習慣，她坦白說：<span class=\"red\">「永遠都不會慣，大家不同背景，其他人年紀大我好多，又要講好多中文。我十四歲去美國，英文好流利，好似母語，講中文就要諗吓。」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/tmp_images/article_multimedia_24000/23637/2_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Ftmp_images%2Farticle_multimedia_24000%2F23637%2F2_n.jpg&h=e98cccd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5631b0e48c1ec745f94ddf9cc2004932f54d2b2","tid":2429732,"uid":33939,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:45:28.000Z","msg":"又文革式批鬥？"},{"pid":"b12b6318b9773cf3449c0aa9c8680f47f2ab7dcd","tid":2429732,"uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"d5631b0e48c1ec745f94ddf9cc2004932f54d2b2","tid":2429732,"uid":33939,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:45:28.000Z","msg":"又文革式批鬥？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:45:51.000Z","msg":"所以唔好停，繼續比油就得"},{"pid":"ad1a6f54838d471d2f41796460834857afc762d3","tid":2429732,"uid":57460,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:46:26.000Z","msg":"政府打算幾時取締design thinking、Kanban board同retrospective，用到大量post it"},{"pid":"bbcd29518573552dff8de305f70f7bf92afaf7c9","tid":2429732,"uid":167469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5631b0e48c1ec745f94ddf9cc2004932f54d2b2","tid":2429732,"uid":33939,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-0